{"word":"G3332 - μεταίρω - metaírō - met-ah'-ee-ro - Depart","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μεταίρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">metaírō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">met-ah'-ee-ro</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Depart</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - புறப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to lift up and remove from one place to another, to transfer,"},{"paragraph":"2. to go away, depart"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3326 - μετά - metá - met-ah'/3326\">G3326</a> and <a href=\"#/G142 - αἴρω - aírō - ah'-ee-ro/142\">G142</a>; to <i>betake</i> oneself, that is, <i>remove</i> (locally): - depart.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}